⍝ BracketIndex.tc
⍝ ═══════════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A nonscalar, I/J simple nonneg integer arrays
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ catenated shapes of the index arrays
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ sum of the ranks of the index arrays
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (5 6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      I ← 1+3∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,2) (,0 1 0 0 0)    ⍝ 2-element index, values 1..5
      J ← 1+5∣|⎕RVAL 1 (,3) (,0 1 0 0 0)    ⍝ 3-element index, values 1..6
      Z ← A[I;J]
      (⍴Z) ≡ (⍴I),⍴J
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,(⍴⍴I)+⍴⍴J
1
